+- [VERIFIED] The fixed gain currency on that branch is
+  `coefficient shrinkage in the fixed localized LEI balance`.
+- [INFERRED] This sharpens the primary endpoint memo:
+  the branch is not merely aiming at concentration exclusion in the abstract;
+  it is asking whether a reformulation can improve the inherited local
+  concentration-exclusion ledger by lowering the effective cutoff-flux cost in
+  the same CKN-style localized LEI package.
