+# Exploration 001 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Freeze one primary endpoint family, one backup endpoint family, one intended
+solution class, and one localization regime for the active reformulation-audit
+chain.
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the active step goal, run-009 chain materials, and the inherited
+  endpoint-freezing record.
+- Separate theorem endpoints from mechanism language.
+- Keep only the smallest endpoint pair that stays on the inherited LEI / CKN
+  floor.
+- Label substantive claims `[VERIFIED]`, `[INFERRED]`, or `[PROPOSED]`.
+
+## Evidence Read
+
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-013/GOAL.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/controller/decisions/decision-021.md`
