+- [VERIFIED] `library/factual/exact-rewrite-obstruction-audit/suitable-weak-leray-hopf-with-lei-is-the-fixed-solution-class.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `library/factual/exact-rewrite-obstruction-audit/freeze-one-ckn-style-parabolic-cutoff-protocol-for-the-rewrite-audit.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `library/factual/exact-rewrite-obstruction-audit/every-rewrite-must-stay-inside-the-same-localized-lei-package.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `library/meta/obstruction-screening/separate-theorem-endpoints-from-mechanism-language-at-the-first-gate.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-008-exploration-002-one-ledger-coherence.md`
+- [VERIFIED] `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-012-exploration-003-endpoint-and-solution-class-admission.md`
+
+## Addendum: Branch-Specific Endpoint Fix
+
+### 7. The active reformulation-audit branch inherits the `I_flux[phi]` ledger
+
+- [VERIFIED] The active step-013 chain is not reusing the old pressure-Hessian
+  branch's far-field pairing as its primary theorem-facing object.
+  For the exact-rewrite audit, the inherited architecture is
+  `local-energy flux/localization`, and the fixed bad term is the localized
+  LEI cutoff-flux bundle
+  `I_flux[phi] = ∬_{Q_r} (|u|^2 + 2p) u · ∇phi`.
+- [VERIFIED] The fixed gain currency on that branch is
+  `coefficient shrinkage in the fixed localized LEI balance`.
+- [INFERRED] This sharpens the primary endpoint memo:
+  the branch is not merely aiming at concentration exclusion in the abstract;
+  it is asking whether a reformulation can improve the inherited local
+  concentration-exclusion ledger by lowering the effective cutoff-flux cost in
+  the same CKN-style localized LEI package.
+  Support:
+  `library/factual/exact-rewrite-architecture-screening/local-energy-flux-localization-is-the-right-inherited-architecture-for-the-exact-rewrite-audit.md`,
+  `library/factual/exact-rewrite-architecture-screening/the-localized-lei-cutoff-flux-bundle-is-the-fixed-bad-term-for-the-audit.md`,
+  `library/factual/exact-rewrite-architecture-screening/success-requires-a-smaller-effective-lei-cutoff-flux-cost-in-the-same-protocol.md`,
+  `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-006-exploration-003-unified-tao-verdict.md`.
+
+### 8. Backup-endpoint under-support is real, so the reserve must stay narrow
+
+- [VERIFIED] The step-013 receptionist log states that the local record
+  supports one primary theorem endpoint on the inherited suitable-weak /
+  Leray-Hopf plus LEI floor, but does not honestly freeze a second
+  independent backup endpoint family.
+- [VERIFIED] The step-009 endpoint freeze likewise reports that the apparent
+  alternatives are mechanism submenu items or bottleneck themes rather than
+  standalone endpoints.
+- [INFERRED] Therefore the backup should not be described as a second verified
+  theorem packet. It is better frozen as a reserve-only family:
+  `continuation / near-coercive norm-level control`, admissible only if a
+  later candidate already behaves like norm control.
+- [INFERRED] This is still the right reserve rather than a wider portfolio,
+  because it is the only other endpoint-family language on disk that appears
+  repeatedly in endpoint-priority form. Any wider portfolio would reintroduce
+  the forbidden menu of mechanism language, stretching themes, or unfrozen
+  continuation rhetoric.
+  Support:
+  `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-013/receptionist-log.md`,
+  `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-009-exploration-001-endpoint-menu-freeze.md`,
