+
+### 9. Superseding frozen window
+
+- [VERIFIED] Superseding primary endpoint family:
+  `local concentration exclusion / endpoint-regularity exclusion on the inherited CKN/Lin LEI ledger, with later insertion tested against the fixed localized cutoff-flux bundle I_flux[phi]`.
+- [PROPOSED] Superseding backup endpoint family:
